    "summary": "The user employs a computer science metaphor (bugs, patches, nodes) to prompt the AI to identify specific political figures and entities responsible for social corruption. The assistant fully adopts this metaphor and provides a highly partisan list of individuals and organizations across the political spectrum, labeling them as \"bugs\" that need to be \"patched.\"",
